4) kubectl apply -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kubernetes/ingress-nginx/controller-v0.35.0/deploy/static/provider/baremetal/deploy.yaml
5) https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nopp/labs/master/demo/ingress.yaml
6) Install nginx no node e configurar o proxy_pass para o ipDoNode:portaDoSVCdoIngress
7) nova app
kubectl create deployment --image nginx my-nginx
kubectl expose deployment my-nginx --port=80
8) lembrar de editar o ingress :D e adicionar app.demo.carlosmalucelli.com
